{"tid":2364034,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"催眠學係咪一切神秘學的基礎？","createTime":"2021-01-12T15:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T16:13:44.000Z","uid":389615,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da184738855133311b94ad535031ec15175e57e3","tid":2364034,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"催眠是使用暗示等方法，讓我們進入放鬆、專注、注意力高度集中的類似睡眠卻並非睡眠的狀態，也就是催眠狀態。<br />\n<br />\n當身體及意識處於催眠狀態，潛意識便較容易接收提示，這可以讓我們與潛意識進行溝通。<br />\n<br />\n具體催眠的應用和幫助：<br />\n1）記憶回溯<br />\n2）麻醉止痛。在麻醉藥面世前做手術，催眠止痛係其中一項麻碎止痛方式。<br />\n3）醫治心理疾病，如焦慮等。<br />\n4）戒壞習慣<br />\n5）幫助入睡<br />\n6）減肥<br />\n<br />\n在神秘學中，催眠可以向自己潛意識溝通，然後潛意識再向自己靈魂溝通，自己靈魂向靈界溝通，達到通靈、前世回溯效果。<br />\n<br />\n在佛教，有類似概念，叫禪定。指因禪定力而得到超越凡人的神秘力量，叫神通。禪定同催眠不同，但都係與潛意識溝通的方法。<br />\n<br />\n倒底催眠所達致的神通或通靈，係真通靈，還是大腦潛意識作崇。大家有待探討。目前主流相信係潛意識的幻想。不過，能夠掌握催眠術的人並不多，期待有更多人學懂它，並探討呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n1）英國老婦手術拒絕麻醉 靠自我催眠克服痛楚<br />\n<a href=\"https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJkFdV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.huanqiu.com%2Farticle%2F9CaKrnJkFdV&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=7eda819c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJkFdV</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2008-07-09/113014138492s.shtml?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fo%2F2008-07-09%2F113014138492s.shtml%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=460509cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2008-07-09/113014138492s.shtml?from=wap</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2008/04/080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fchina%2Flifeintheuk%2Fstory%2F2008%2F04%2F080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=5ae66e87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/china/lifeintheuk/story/2008/04/080424_hypnotistoperation.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n2) Hypnosis - Hypnotherapy<br />\n<a href=\"https://stanfordhealthcare.org/medical-treatments/h/hypnosis.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstanfordhealthcare.org%2Fmedical-treatments%2Fh%2Fhypnosis.html&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=54973c9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stanfordhealthcare.org/medical-treatments/h/hypnosis.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stanfordhealthcare.org/medical-treatments/h/hypnosis/what-to-expect.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstanfordhealthcare.org%2Fmedical-treatments%2Fh%2Fhypnosis%2Fwhat-to-expect.html&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=4ba284d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stanfordhealthcare.org/medical-treatments/h/hypnosis/what-to-expect.html</a><br />\n<br />\n3) Study identifies brain areas altered during hypnotic trances<br />\n<a href=\"https://med.stanford.edu/news/all-news/2016/07/study-identifies-brain-areas-altered-during-hypnotic-trances.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmed.stanford.edu%2Fnews%2Fall-news%2F2016%2F07%2Fstudy-identifies-brain-areas-altered-during-hypnotic-trances.html&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=b5231749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://med.stanford.edu/news/all-news/2016/07/study-identifies-brain-areas-altered-during-hypnotic-trances.html</a><br />\n<br />\n4）Wikipedia<br />\n前世回溯<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E5%9B%9E%E6%BA%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%2596%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25BA%25AF&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=885f9c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E5%9B%9E%E6%BA%AF</a><br />\n神通<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%A5%9E%E9%80%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%2580%259A&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=449dd0eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%A5%9E%E9%80%9A</a><br />\n禪定<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A6%AA%E5%AE%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AE%259A&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=2823fdad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A6%AA%E5%AE%9A</a><br />\n5）"},{"pid":"a8b92a46764e758cb0204ff62c643c3177942ff2","tid":2364034,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:06:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>催眠是使用暗示等方法，讓我們進入放鬆、專注、注意力高度集中的類似睡眠卻並非睡眠的狀態，也就是催眠狀態。<br />\n<br />\n當身體及意識處於催眠狀態，潛意識便較容易接收提示，這可以讓我們與潛意識進行溝通。<br />\n<br />\n具體催眠的應用和幫助：<br />\n1）記憶回溯<br />\n2）麻醉止痛。在麻醉藥面世前做手術，催眠止痛係其中一項麻碎止痛方式。<br />\n3）醫治心理疾病，如焦慮等。<br />\n4）戒壞習慣<br />\n5）幫助入睡<br />\n6）減肥<br />\n<br />\n在神秘學中，催眠可以向自己潛意識溝通，然後潛意識再向自己靈魂溝通，自己靈魂向靈界溝通，達到通靈、前世回溯效果。<br />\n<br />\n在佛教，有類似概念，叫禪定。指因禪定力而得到超越凡人的神秘力量，叫神通。禪定同催眠不同，但都係與潛意識溝通的方法。<br />\n<br />\n倒底催眠所達致的神通或通靈，係真通靈，還是大腦潛意識作崇。大家有待探討。目前主流相信係潛意識的幻想。不過，能夠掌握催眠術的人並不多，期待有更多人學懂它，並探討呢件事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考：<br />\n1）英國老婦手術拒絕麻醉 靠自我催眠克服痛楚<br />\n<a href=\"https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJkFdV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.huanqiu.com%2Farticle%2F9CaKrnJkFdV&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=7eda819c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJkFdV</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.sina.com.cn/o/2008-07-09/113014138492s.shtml?from=wap\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.cn%2Fo%2F2008-07-09%2F113014138492s.shtml%3Ffrom%3Dwap&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=460509cf\" data-auto-link target