前世回溯<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E5%9B%9E%E6%BA%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2589%258D%25E4%25B8%2596%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25BA%25AF&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=885f9c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%96%E5%9B%9E%E6%BA%AF</a><br />\n神通<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%A5%9E%E9%80%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%2580%259A&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=449dd0eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%A5%9E%E9%80%9A</a><br />\n禪定<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A6%AA%E5%AE%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25A6%25AA%25E5%25AE%259A&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=2823fdad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%A6%AA%E5%AE%9A</a><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n5）HKMA 催眠高等文憑課程簡介<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkma.org.hk/modular/adh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkma.org.hk%2Fmodular%2Fadh%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=b5e50b67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkma.org.hk/modular/adh/</a><br />\n<br />\n6) 催眠術&mdash;&mdash;聖經所稱的「迷術」<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinesechristiandiscernment.net/hypnosis.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinesechristiandiscernment.net%2Fhypnosis.htm&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=32b8c3da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinesechristiandiscernment.net/hypnosis.htm</a><br />\n（文中提到，斯和凱瑟琳的例子並不獨特，也有其他研究指出人在接受催眠後產生靈異能力。）<br />\n（文中提到，很多前生回溯是在不預期的情形下突然發生的，有催眠師本來不相信輪回，但是因為太經常看見病人在催眠下發現自己的前生，所以無法不檢討自己的世界觀）<br />\n<br />\n7）基督徒可以練瑜伽、外丹功， 或受催眠嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://joy.org.tw/file/holyspirit/393/201006-393-60.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjoy.org.tw%2Ffile%2Fholyspirit%2F393%2F201006-393-60.pdf&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=7d11432a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://joy.org.tw/file/holyspirit/393/201006-393-60.pdf</a><br />\n（文中強調催眠具通靈功能，並以基督教方式批判視之為魔鬼邪靈）"},{"pid":"d89f03529fdd7bc1b80b8bb448173ad0b75ded15","tid":2364034,"uid":388788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:06:37.000Z","msg":"想學"},{"pid":"5df1b40ebb3f7422c3b59a3fe3cc907521f0ddcc","tid":2364034,"uid":304014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T16:13:44.000Z","msg":"催眠hypnosis，其實喺心理學上仲係好controversial"}]}